- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science): The paper discusses pattern-matching against unfree data types, which can involve complex logical reasoning. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The paper discusses pattern-matching against various data types, including sets and graphs, which are common data structures. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering): The paper discusses modularization of pattern-matching, which is a software engineering concept. 
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory): The paper discusses pattern-matching, which is a fundamental concept in formal languages and automata theory.
